with version stable 1.2
with base    acl
with role    utility
with trait   console library makej multilib-concurrent
with source  ftp://ftp.berlios.de/pub/sfind/sfind-$VERSION.tar.bz2
with info    good 20120705
with info    last 20060918
with info    cite 'another implementation of the find utility
It is a fully POSIX.1-2001 compliant implementation of the find utility.
It implements features like -ls and -exec program [argument ...] {} +
(the latter is the POSIX built in xargs).
It has no limitations on path length.
Directory loops caused by hard-linked directories are handled gracefully.'

build(){
 make &&
 make install INS_BASE=$DESTDIR/usr
}
